msgid ""
"The digiKam **Apply Texture** tool applies decorative textures to an image."
msgstr ""
"**Applica trama** è uno strumento di digiKam serve ad applicare delle trame "
"decorative a un'immagine."

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:25
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "By adding texture to your image, whether color or black and white, you "
#| "can make it look like an oil painting on canvas, an Old Masters etching, "
#| "a Pop Art portrait composed of enlarged half-tone dots, or even a mural "
#| "on a brick wall. The :menuselection:`Decorate --> Apply Texture` menu "
